\nc<>What's wrong, senpai? You've been looking around nervously
since earlier.

\nc<>Ta-da! I borrowed a hallucination magic tool from ○○-chan.
\nc<>Now, please use this and become a dog, senpai.

\nc<>(I'm not even human anymore, being turned into a dog.) (I
can't believe it has come to this...)

\nc<>Oh my~? You seem quite troubled, senpai. You've been
affected by the succubus' pheromones, haven't you?

\nc<>I wouldn't ask you to do something so perverted in a normal
state.
\nc<>(That's right. Because I've been done by an incubus...)

\nc<>As I thought, this kind of outfit suits you, senpai, like a
female dog.

\nc<>(Because of my tail, I feel discomfort in my butt...
ugh...)

\nc<>There's still something I need to put on, senpai. Please
spread your legs quickly.

\nc<>Do we absolutely have to do that? Like we did last time
with the collar--

\nc<>I thought I would give you a little lick, but your clit is
already so hard.
\nc<>(This, sticking closely to my clit) (It's sucking on it...!)

\nc<>Finally, the preparations are done. Well then, let's go for
a fun walk today, senpai.

\nc<>Senpai, if you keep stopping like that, we won't be able to

\nc<>Hey, didn't I just warn you earlier? Illusion magic

discomfort.
\nc<>Well done. Hehe. You have a cute little dog.
\nc<>Let's finish our walk with that momentum.

\nc<>(This child is intentionally pulling the leash and
stimulating their clit.)

like it...)
